channel.title: MoparScape Webclient Error?
channel.description:
Whenever I try to run MoparScape Webclient, I get this error:
PS: Sorry if you can't read it, this is the color of the text (If you can't read it, try highlighting it.)
Sorry, an error has occured whilst loading RuneScape
To fix this try the following (in order):
1. Try closing ALL open web-browsers, and reloading
2. Try clearing your web-browsers cache from tools->internet options
3. Try using a different game-world
4. Try rebooting your computer
5. Try selecting a different version of Java from the play-game menu
Also, at the bottom of the screen it says "Error: loaderror bobConnecting to fileserver 10".
I don't understand, it was just working, then I try to go on a different server and I get this error. Any help???
